   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2" image="QN_april.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-" mid="72" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Try talking to <FONT color=#a82424>April</FONT>. I'm training her to collection information recently so she might know something... Well, she better do or she will get into trouble.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2-a" mid="73" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>What brings you here?<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Tell her what Vernicka said.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2-b" mid="74" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>…President Vernicka wanted you to get information from me? He also said that I'd get into trouble if I didn't have the information?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2-c" mid="75" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>All I wanted was to be an ordinary history enthusiast. How did I end up getting spotted by President Vernicka and get spy training from him...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2-d" mid="76" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>I don't know what trouble I would get into if I didn't have any information. Thankfully, I have done some investigation on the matter you're asking.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2-e" mid="78" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>After Tryan died, <FONT color=#a82424>Holy Edart Empire</FONT> has sent new troops to manage <FONT color=#a82424>Tryan's Territory</FONT>. But there seems to have been a theft case among the soldiers there and those remaining in <FONT color=#a82424>Wasteland Battlefield</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2-f" mid="79" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Some soldiers even died while trying to stop the thief so there are rumours that maybe it's a newly occurred Child.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2-g" mid="80" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>I heard a low Child has been sent to investigate on this matter. He has been sent to investigate <FONT color=#a82424>Retrograde Highland</FONT> in the Distorted Zone.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-3" mid="81" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Could the investigator be after Grele? If it is a Child from the central authorities, he wouldn't know my face. Maybe I should meet him directly.) </FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-3" image="QW_111.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
